snippet.title: 【Vextorial】 | MULTI-DIMENSIONAL Puzzle Game | "This Game Blew My Mind"
snippet.description:
🚩Wishlist on Steam now! 🚩
👆 https://store.steampowered.com/app/3068710/Vextorial/

In Vextorial you can:
‣ Manipulate gravity of the environment
‣ Switch to different Planes in a 3-dimensional field
‣ Solve Meta-Puzzles unravelled in later stages of the game
‣ Discover the Lore of the enigmatic realm

Follow for more!
